## Limitations

The report is limited by the availability of up-to-date data and the evolving nature of military policies. Some sources may not reflect the most current practices or outcomes of implemented strategies. Additionally, the complexity of military culture and the confidentiality of certain military operations may restrict access to comprehensive data.